\id FRT
\mt1 Anutuna Ufa
\ip First Edition of New Testament published 1983 400 copies
\ip This revised edition plus 5 Old Testament books published 2017 450 copies
\ib
\ip © 2017 Wycliffe Bible Translators, Inc.
\ib
\ip This book is a translation of the New Testament and five Old Testament books into the Binumarien language which is spoken by approximately 1000 people who live 20 nautical miles east of Kainantu in the Eastern Highlands Province of Papua New Guinea.
\ip For this edition, a minor revision was done on the 1983 Binumarien New Tesatment and the 2003 publication of Genesis, Exodus, and Psalms. Proverbs and Esther, which were translated since then, are also included. In the revision process, tone makers and dashes were removed from most words for easier reading and some long words were broken into shorter words. In addition, the text has undergone minimal revisions of various kinds. New maps, illustrations, and pictures were included to aid understanding. A topical index was included for Bible study.
\ip To date the Binumarien people continue their efforts towards completing their translation of the full Bible.
\imt2 Amuaqira Ufa
\ip Ooqeennaa tamummaqarausa ufa akara rusa Heebeeru ufakiqari akara riqau. Yisufa aqbee nari ufa Arammaika ufakiqari qimarufaqa Fuka Moodaanaki Kirana akara rusa Kirika ufakiqari akara riqau. Maqee kaqi Kirika ufaki marifaqa aiqama maqannaasa nari ufakiqari quandasee akara ridaqa. Afaqinnaasa ufakiqari faqa indaaru akara rumasoona 1984 aukuannaki maraqau. Tamummaqarausa ufa moodaannai qisauku (5) buka faqa akara rumaqaafanoo maridanoo. Mifa inni dadaaqinaqa, innee Anutufa Isaraee maqannaasaki auqoo ainainausara amiqimmasee irifaranoo.
\ip Aiqama fookufa taikeenoo, qoodaa kai kaqi uqaqaafanoo maridanoo. Maaqira ququsaki mari ufafa ( ) inni irirana dadaaqianifeera papiqa akara rimariasa uqaidaqa. Kaifaa maaqira ququsaki mari ufafa [ ] ooqai indaaru maa papiqana akara rusa kooroo ira ufa maaqira ququsaki akara rumaqoofanoo marinau. Kirika ufaki sia amiqimmasee koorooina faqa mi ququsanaki koorooidaqa. Maa bukana atinni weesa nambaqa faqa buka auqu qusa uqaqaafanoo maridanoo. Mataioona qusa auqu Mat miqirafauqa faqa piksaauqa faqa Isaraee maqannaasa maqa maaqa faqa inni dadaaqianifeera akara rumaqaafanoo maridanoo. 
